# - Oracle fuzz: 1000 iterations, 0% exact match, 0 panics, 0 exit mismatches
# - Receipts: 22 receipt files covering all 12 sealed courts
# - Kani proofs: 13 BMC + 8 Prusti contracts + 14 runtime = 35 total
